: Detecting and anonymizing financial information is essential. For example, validators can identify price quotes in various currencies to ensure financial data is protected. The following Python code demonstrates how to use Guardrails to detect price quotes in text:
Input and Output Handling: Ensuring the data handled by AI agents is appropriate and secure is vital. Here are some techniques:: AI agents should only discuss relevant topics. For example, an organization may restrict AI agents from discussing certain topics like politics, religion, sports, entertainments, or sensitive company information. One can use a LLM to enforce these restrictions and ensure the content is related to the intended subject. The following Python code demonstrates how to use OpenAI GPT-4o-mini to restrict content not to a specific topic (e.g., sports):
